---
import { site } from '../../config/site';
---

<section id="lavori" class="py-14 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-warm-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Sfumatura decorativa laterale -->
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-1/3 bg-gradient-to-l from-warm-100/60 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">

    <p class="text-brand text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-3">Portfolio</p>
    <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-ink-900 text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-5 sm:mb-6 leading-snug">I nostri lavori</h2>

    <div class="w-12 h-px bg-warm-300 mx-auto mb-6"></div>

    <p class="text-ink-600 leading-relaxed mb-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg">
      Migliaia di traslochi, centinaia di famiglie e aziende che ci hanno affidato le loro cose più care.
    </p>
    <p class="text-ink-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 sm:mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto text-base">
      Guarda le nostre foto su Facebook: vedrai come trattiamo casa tua con la stessa cura che riserveresti tu.
    </p>

    <a
      href={site.social.facebook}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-brand hover:bg-brand-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold transition-all duration-200 shadow-[0_4px_16px_rgba(191,40,43,0.28)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_22px_rgba(191,40,43,0.38)] hover:-translate-y-px w-full sm:w-auto"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
      </svg>
      Guarda i nostri lavori su Facebook
    </a>

  </div>
</section>
